OL,3,CElderly woman was theft victim on day
OL,4,Cshe was fatally injured
OL,6,FPolice say an elderly woman who died
OL,7,Ftwo months after being found seriously
OL,8,Finjured had been a victim of a theft
OL,9,Fon the day she was hurt.
OL,11,FElizabeth Clark, 91, was discovered
OL,12,Finjured at her home in Peveril Close,
OL,13,FKiveton Park, Rotherham on 11
OL,14,FSeptember last year. She died in
OL,15,Fhospital on 12 November.
OL,17,FSouth Yorkshire Police are treating
OL,18,Fher death as murder.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/4
