FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1773770757
OL,3,CElderly woman was theft victim on day
OL,4,Cshe was fatally injured
OL,6,FThe force said the investigation,
OL,7,Fincluding CCTV trawls, house-to-house
OL,8,Fenquiries and forensic analysis, had
OL,9,Festablished Ms Clark, known as
OL,10,F"Betty", was injured on 10 September.
OL,12,FOfficers say her bank card was stolen
OL,13,Fthe same day and was used for multiple
OL,14,Ftransactions between 10 and 16
OL,15,FSeptember.
OL,17,FA spokesperson told ITV Calendar they
OL,18,Fwere working through theories and
OL,19,Fcould not confirm how Ms Clark
OL,20,Fsustained her injuries.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
