FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1773770757
OL,3,CElderly woman was theft victim on day
OL,4,Cshe was fatally injured
OL,6,FDet Insp Adam Watkinson appealed for
OL,7,Finformation.
OL,9,FHe said: "Any information, no matter
OL,10,Fhow small, could be vital to our
OL,11,Finvestigation.
OL,13,F"Betty was well-loved within her local
OL,14,Fcommunity, by her many friends, family
OL,15,Fand neighbours, and our priority
OL,16,Fremains the same - to find answers."
OL,18,FA 47-year-old man who was arrested on
OL,19,Fsuspicion of murder in December,
OL,20,Fremains on police bail at this time.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/4
